OL,3,CSeaside tourist attraction has #51
OL,4,Cmillion council debt written off
OL,6,FWords by Sarah Booker-Lewis, Local
OL,7,FDemocracy Reporter
OL,9,FA debt of more than #50 million, owed
OL,10,Fby the i360 tourist attraction to
OL,11,FBrighton and Hove City Council, has
OL,12,Fbeen written off so administrators can
OL,13,Fsell it.
OL,15,FBrighton and Hove City Council leader
OL,16,Fcouncillor Bella Sankey said this
OL,17,Fwould be the "least worst" option and
OL,18,Fwas "incredulous" at the position the
OL,19,Fcouncil was in, with taxpayers taking
OL,20,Fthe burden.
