OL,6,F"While this may be the least-worst
OL,7,Foption, I understand why residents are
OL,8,Fso incredulous that this situation has
OL,9,Fcome to pass ` I'm incredulous and
OL,10,Fangry."
OL,12,FShe said that the amount of money
OL,13,Fgoing towards the "reckless venture"
OL,14,Fwas sickening as she backed an inquiry
OL,15,Finto the decision which she said was
OL,16,Fmade at the expense of residents.
