OL,6,FNo buyer could be found to buy the
OL,7,Fi360 before it went into
OL,8,Fadministration last month when the
OL,9,Fbusiness was unable to service its
OL,10,Fdebts.
OL,12,FMore than 100 staff lost their jobs in
OL,13,Fthe week before Christmas.
OL,15,FThe sum owed to the council is more
OL,16,Fthan #51 million including interest.
OL,18,FThe council brokered the loan from the
OL,19,FPublic Works Loan Board and still owes
OL,20,F#32 million or about #2.2 million a
OL,21,Fyear over the next 16 years until 2041.
