OL,6,FThe Labour deputy leader of the
OL,7,Fcouncil Jacob Taylor has been working
OL,8,Fwith the administrators to deal with
OL,9,Fthe "bad hand" the council has been
OL,10,Fdealt.
OL,12,FCouncillor Taylor said: "It was with
OL,13,Fno pleasure that any of us saw the
OL,14,Fattraction shut and 109 people made
OL,15,Fredundant at the end of last year.
