OL,6,F"We face a set of relatively
OL,7,Funappetising options but it is really
OL,8,Fimportant that we make the decision
OL,9,Fand take the option that this best for
OL,10,Fthe city and I believe what is
OL,11,Frecommended is the best option.
OL,13,F"The council could take it on as the
OL,14,Fmain creditor. If that were the case,
OL,15,Fthe council would have to plough in
OL,16,Ftaxpayers' money to get it running
OL,17,Fagain."
